              en: 'Dr. Surangama Yadav: Born: 19 June 1970. Born in Uttar Pradesh. Famous Haiku collections include \'Yaadon ke Panchhi\', \'Bhav Prakoshth\', \'Gaayegi Sadi\'. Honored with \'Ramdhari Singh Dinkar Award\'.'
